{"tid":1377962,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"7月30日全民罷工","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T11:53:14.000Z","uid":258758,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"59d5aa1fb492ceaa4bbace302f1967fdf7675fde","tid":1377962,"uid":258758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"建議7月30日罷工嘅全港市民<br />\n建議一同癱瘓<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">金鐘、旺角、九龍塘</span></span><br />\n我地好需要你地發發呢個不合作運動 不論你係公私營機構 學生 定師奶仔<br />\n因為呢場仗我地一旦輸左 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港將會萬劫不復</span></span><br />\n1. 去過示威嘅都面臨被檢控<br />\n2. 愈來愈多嘅不利港政策 以及進一步收窄港人自由 eg. 智慧燈柱、信用評級<br />\n3. 警黑合作無間 正式淪陷成為大灣區一個小城市 失去所有港英政府時所建立並引以自豪嘅優勢<br />\n4. 承上 到時我地嘅一舉一動都會被監控 就算到時你有咩不滿你都只可以被逼接受 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失去所有言論及集會自由</span></span><br />\n咁多位有小朋友嘅家長 你地真係想你地下一代生活係呢個咁嘅地方?<br />\n咁多位當年偷渡黎港嘅上一代 當初就係因為香港好境你地先黎香港 你地真係忍心香港因為你地嘅沈默 而斷送你地嘅孫仔孫女嘅前途?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">或者你地都聽唔入耳 但係對於年輕人黎講 我地仲有大把日子要捱<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而香港就係我地嘅家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我係度呼籲黎緊星期二(7月30日)香港全民罷罷工逼使政府回應五大訢求!<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n一個都不能少 <br />\n不流血，不受傷，不被捕<br />\n不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"9bd6af1443cb53bfb52797a18d2c28287f4ffb47","tid":1377962,"uid":258758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47cba900f786b53d183a2ccf85db4fcce55a489a","tid":1377962,"uid":258758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:56:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2df5ca6bd06d8bd752531a65c226426827cc450f","tid":1377962,"uid":258758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2991be47c2ed64152feec8d46f6e439b2f42ba70","tid":1377962,"uid":258758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921f14318709aacf6576d7e1a3bf6fbf6fcd7e38","tid":1377962,"uid":258758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:57:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac640c0d7781ff7890f33839e48d824f798bf2b","tid":1377962,"uid":147017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:57:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19c6729dfa9850fa9faf647d85fb7ad588b9a9b3","tid":1377962,"uid":285007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:57:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e39d72aff69c93c9f9706bb9fd6241fe0c895c86","tid":1377962,"uid":258758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696126927838cd86185f3433c10e4ad9ffbb07f2","tid":1377962,"uid":249187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34200a56b043f45f2e130c778cb0aa2c3fbc386","tid":1377962,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:57:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f5c681554570d304dcca21a62443873ff0a7b35","tid":1377962,"uid":258758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"入黎一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18f6d7f0f96878e04177c2acc97bd6c319323f1","tid":1377962,"uid":108224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite